---
// src/pages/panel-upgrade-investment-roi.astro
import { getImage } from "astro:assets";
import Layout from "../../layouts/Layout.astro";
import investmentHero from "../../assets/images/investment-panelupgrade.jpg";

const pageTitle = "Is a Panel Upgrade a Good Investment? | ROI & Home Value";
const pageDescription =
  "Discover the return on investment (ROI) of an electrical panel upgrade in Las Vegas, including increased home value, insurance savings, and enhanced safety.";

const hero = await getImage({ src: investmentHero });
const heroBg = `linear-gradient(rgba(17,94,89,0.45), rgba(17,94,89,0.15)), url(${hero.src})`; // teal overlay + image
---

<Layout title={pageTitle} description={pageDescription}>
  <main class="bg-white text-gray-800">
    <!-- Page Header -->
    <section
      class="page-header-investment text-white"
      style={{ backgroundImage: heroBg }}
    >
      <div
        class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-20 md:py-24 text-center"
      >
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-6xl font-extrabold leading-tight mb-4">
          Is an Electrical Panel Upgrade a Good Investment?
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg md:text-xl max-w-3xl mx-auto text-teal-100">
          Beyond the immediate
          <a
            href="/cost-of-panel-upgrade-las-vegas/"
            class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">cost</a
          >, a panel upgrade offers a significant return on investment through
          safety, home value, and future-readiness.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Main Content Area -->
    <div>
      <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-16 xl:py-24">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
          <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none mb-12">
            <p>
              When considering a major home improvement project, it's natural to
              think about the return on investment (ROI). While some upgrades
              are purely cosmetic, an electrical panel upgrade is a foundational
              investment that provides tangible returns in several key areas.
              It's not just an expense; it's a strategic improvement to your
              property's core infrastructure.
            </p>
          </div>

          <!-- Investment Points Section -->
          <div class="space-y-8">
            <!-- Point 1: Home Value -->
            <div
              class="investment-card p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex items-start"
            >
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 investment-icon-container rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mr-6"
              >
                <svg
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  focusable="false"
                  class="w-8 h-8"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M3 12l2-2m0 0l7-7 7 7M5 10v10a1 1 0 001 1h3m10-11l2 2m-2-2v10a1 1 0 01-1 1h-3m-6 0a1 1 0 001-1v-4a1 1 0 011-1h2a1 1 0 011 1v4a1 1 0 001 1m-6 0h6"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                  Directly Increases Home Value
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-lg">
                  A modern, 200-amp electrical panel is a major selling point.
                  For potential buyers, it signals that the home is
                  well-maintained and ready for modern demands like EV chargers
                  and smart home technology. It removes a major objection during
                  home inspections and can lead to a higher final sale price.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Point 2: Insurance Savings -->
            <div
              class="investment-card p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex items-start"
            >
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 investment-icon-container rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mr-6"
              >
                <svg
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  focusable="false"
                  class="w-8 h-8"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M9 12l2 2 4-4m5.618-4.016A11.955 11.955 0 0112 2.944a11.955 11.955 0 01-8.618 3.04A12.02 12.02 0 003 20.944A12.02 12.02 0 0012 22a12.02 12.02 0 009-1.056c.343-.344.65-.724.923-1.138a11.955 11.955 0 01-2.3-5.508 11.955 11.955 0 01.134-4.252z"
                  ></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                  Lowers Your Homeowner's Insurance
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-lg">
                  Insurance companies are all about risk assessment. Replacing
                  an old fuse box or a hazardous panel like an
                  <a
                    href="/dangers-federal-pacific-fpe-panels-las-vegas/"
                    class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">FPE</a
                  >
                  or
                  <a
                    href="/zinsco-panel-dangers-las-vegas/"
                    class="text-accent font-semibold hover:underline">Zinsco</a
                  >
                  model drastically reduces the risk of an electrical fire. Many
                  insurers offer significant discounts for this proactive safety
                  measure.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Point 3: Prevents Costly Repairs -->
            <div
              class="investment-card p-8 rounded-lg shadow-sm flex items-start"
            >
              <div
                class="flex-shrink-0 investment-icon-container rounded-full w-16 h-16 flex items-center justify-center mr-6"
              >
                <svg
                  aria-hidden="true"
                  focusable="false"
                  class="w-8 h-8"
                  fill="none"
                  stroke="currentColor"
                  viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                >
                  <path
                    stroke-linecap="round"
                    stroke-linejoin="round"
                    stroke-width="2"
                    d="M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z"></path>
                </svg>
              </div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900">
                  Prevents Damage to Expensive Electronics
                </h3>
                <p class="text-gray-600 mt-3 text-lg">
                  An old, unstable panel can deliver inconsistent power, causing
                  surges that can damage sensitive electronics like computers,
                  TVs, and smart appliances. A new panel provides clean, stable
                  power that protects your valuable devices from premature
                  failure.
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <!-- Final CTA -->
    <div
      class="text-center bg-gray-800 text-white py-16 xl:py-24"
    >
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-extrabold">
        Invest in Your Home's Most Critical System
      </h2>
      <p class="mt-4 text-lg text-gray-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        An electrical panel upgrade is one of the smartest investments you can
        make, offering returns in safety, value, and peace of mind. Contact us
        to discuss how an upgrade can benefit your property.
      </p>
      <div class="mt-8">
        <a
          href="/company/company/contact-us/"
          class="bg-accent text-black font-bold py-3 px-8 rounded-full text-lg hover:bg-accent-dark transition-transform duration-300 inline-block transform hover:scale-105"
        >
          Get My Free Consultation
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>

<style>
  /* Accent utilities (scoped) */
  .bg-accent {
    background-color: #f1b725;
  } /* amber-400 */
  .text-accent {
    color: #f1b725;
  }
  .border-accent {
    border-color: #f1b725;
  }
  .hover\:bg-accent-dark:hover {
    background-color: #f59e0b;
  } /* amber-500 */
  .ring-accent {
    --tw-ring-color: #f1b725;
  }

  /* Template-specific */
  .page-header-investment {
    background-color: #115e59; /* teal-900 fallback behind the image+overlay */
    background-size: cover;
    background-position: center;
  }
  .investment-card {
    background-color: #f9fafb;
  }
  .investment-icon-container {
    background-color: #14b8a6;
    color: #ffffff;
  }
</style>
